#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.170"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.170:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.170:0.2"
msgid "13. Esanāvagga"
msgstr "13. Searches"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.170:0.3"
msgid "170. Taṇhāsutta"
msgstr "170. Craving"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.58"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.170:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, taṇhā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three cravings."

msgctxt "sn45.170:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "sn45.170:1.3"
msgid "Kāmataṇhā, bhavataṇhā, vibhavataṇhā—"
msgstr ""
"Craving for sensual pleasures, craving to continue existence, and craving to "
"end existence."

msgctxt "sn45.170:1.4"
msgid "imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso taṇhā."
msgstr "These are the three cravings."

msgctxt "sn45.170:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ taṇhānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya "
"pahānāya … pe … ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo."
msgstr ""
"The noble eightfold path should be developed for the direct knowledge, "
"complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these three cravings."

msgctxt "sn45.170:1.6"
msgid "Katamo ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo?"
msgstr "What is the noble eightfold path?"

msgctxt "sn45.170:1.7"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.170:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ taṇhānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya "
"pahānāya … pe … ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the noble eightfold path that should be developed for the direct "
"knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these three "
"cravings.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.170:1.9"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.0"
msgid "Tasināsutta"
msgstr "Thirst"

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, tasinā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three thirsts."

msgctxt "sn45.170:2.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "sn45.170:2.3"
msgid "Kāmatasinā, bhavatasinā, vibhavatasinā."
msgstr ""
"Thirst for sensual pleasures, thirst to continue existence, and thirst to "
"end existence."

msgctxt "sn45.170:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ tasinānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya "
"pahānāya … pe … ."
msgstr ""
"For the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up "
"of these three thirsts …"

msgctxt "sn45.170:2.5"
msgid "rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ…pe…"
msgstr "… which culminates in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion."

msgctxt "sn45.170:2.6"
msgid "amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ…pe…"
msgstr "… which culminates, finishes, and ends in the deathless."

msgctxt "sn45.170:2.7"
msgid "nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ nibbānapabbhāraṃ."
msgstr "… which slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn45.170:2.8"
msgid ""
"Imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ tasinānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya "
"pahānāya …pe…  ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"The noble eightfold path should be developed for the direct knowledge, "
"complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these three thirsts.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.9"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endvagga">
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.10"
msgid "Esanāvaggo sattamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="uddana-intro">
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.11"
msgid "Tassuddānaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.12"
msgid "Esanā vidhā āsavo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.13"
msgid "bhavo ca dukkhatā khilā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.14"
msgid "Malaṃ nīgho ca vedanā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.170:2.15"
msgid "dve taṇhā tasināya cāti."
msgstr ""
